Package mx.org.pescadormvp.core.client.internallinks

Classes for creating application-internal hyperlinks.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InternalLink
    An application-internal link, with data provided by a PescadorMVPPlace.
    IsItem
    An item that may be included in an ItemPanel.
    ItemResources
    General CSS and image resources for item widgets.
    ItemResources.ItemStyle
    General CSS resources for item widgets.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InternalButtonLink
    A button that's a link to a place in the application, and a native hyperlink, too.
    InternalCheckableItemLink
    An item in a menu that leads to a place in the application, is a native hyperlink, and may have a checkmark beside it.
    InternalImageLink
    An image that's a link to a place in the application, and a native hyperlink, too.
    InternalLinkBase
    Logic for creating a link to somewhere in the app, based on a PescadorMVPPlace.
    InternalLinkHTMLRenderer
    Creates a sanitized HTML string for internal links.
    ItemPanel
    A panel widget that can contain items.
